AN ORIGINAL SIN TIE-IN!

Last we checked, Star-Lord, Thanos, and Nova were trapped in the Cancerverse…

But Star-Lord and Thanos seem to be running around just fine.

So what exactly happened to Richard Rider?

2014-10-13|2014-10-19.description:
Kaname vows to sacrifice himself. Yuki vows to sacrifice herself to stop him.

Zero takes a weapon in hand to protect what is dear to him.

Whether parted for eternity or close enough to touch, they each will always desire their beloved…

Chapter Titles

  • Eighty-Ninth Night: The Night Afer Thousands of Nights
  • Ninetieth Night: Falling with You
  • Ninety-First Night: Birds Who Have Forgotten Joyous Songs
  • Ninety-Second Night: A True Knight
  • The Final Night: Vampire Knight

2014-10-27|2014-11-02.description:
KIERON GILLEN has captivated the comics' community with the horror and drama unfolding in the enhanced human warfare of World War II. As the war starts to slide in favor of the Nazis unstoppable Ubers, the Allies strike out with a desperate gamble. They can't match the Uber Battleships one-on-one, but maybe they can use surgical strikes against the mounting tide. Join the legions of readers as the misery of super human warfare continues to unfold.

Available with Regular & Wraparound covers by Caanan White, Propaganda Poster cover by Michael DiPascale, and War Crimes and Blitzkrieg Incentive covers by Caanan White.

This issue consists of a hand painted figurine and a magazine on the issues featured character, Hawkeye.

The Avengers set continues with issue 19, White Pawn - Hawkeye.
2014-11-03|2014-11-09.name: Hawkeye [White Pawn]

2014-11-03|2014-11-09.description: Leo Winters and Requiem have managed to put aside their differences to face the oncoming threat together, but there’s a bigger enemy at play, one that seeks not only to destroy Requiem by any means necessary, but possibly, the world...
2014-11-03|2014-11-09.name: Scorched Earth Part 1 of 3

2014-11-03|2014-11-09.description: The concluding chapter of "The Man Who Quit Being Human" puts Batman in a final, desperate battle with the deadly Mutant. The fate of mankind may be in the balance.
2014-11-03|2014-11-09.name: The Man Who Quit Being Human Chapter 4 of 4

2014-11-10|2014-11-16.description:
Largo Winch goes to London with Dwight Cochrane, Miss Pennywinkle, and Silky, to chair the Board of Big W Group. He hopes to convince Laurent Draillac, French aircraft manufacturer, to enter into a joint venture with his group's aerospace branch.

On the agenda: working meetings and relaxation. Soon the situation gets tricky. Jihadi terrorists, spies and double agents weave a deadly canvas around the beautiful Saide. What happens when, against all odds, the target and the killer fall madly in love with each other?
2014-11-10|2014-11-16.name: Chassé-Croisé

2014-11-10|2014-11-16.description: The danger of Constantine’s journey to Earth 2 is increasing by the second. Now he’s faced with the pressure of having something worth fighting for: his family!
2014-11-10|2014-11-16.name: The Apocalypse Road

2014-11-10|2014-11-16.description:
The perverse “pig-man” unmasked!

A nameless man, scarred from an encounter with the Skin Traders, is wheeled into the hospital—only Leigh Ferguson knows that this John Doe is none other than Arcadia’s most wanted, X! But the sicko surgeon that sliced him up is closing in to finish the job.
2014-11-10|2014-11-16.name: Flesh and Blood Part 3

2014-11-24|2014-11-30.description: After all his adventures across the American continent, after defeating his many enemies, XIII is trying to live a simple life in the house he inherited, where it all started. It’s not always easy – not everyone is happy to have such an infamous man in the area, and his skills are in high demand with some people of varying integrity. His memories are still locked away, too, and some people want to keep it that way…
2014-11-24|2014-11-30.name: The Day of the Mayflower

2014-11-24|2014-11-30.description: The secrets of the House of Grayskull are revealed! Flash back to Prince Adam's childhood, when rebellion struck King Randor's throne. What does this moment in time mean for the future war in Eternia? Find out in this prelude to MASTERS OF THE UNIVERSE: THE ETERNITY WAR #1!
2014-11-24|2014-11-30.name: Stuck in a Moment

volume.name: He-Man and the Masters of the Universe

2014-11-24|2014-11-30.description: The latest stop on Witch Hunter's lost odyssey through time is a September morning in Paris, 1791, not long past the dawn of the French Revolution. With no way of his own to get back to the present, he's forced to rescue an evil witch from Madame Guillotine and spirit her out of France in exchange for her sorcerous one-way ticket to the 21st century. He won't have to rescue her all by himself, though, as he'll have help from someone with a lot of experience in the matter...the legendary Scarlet Pimpernel!

2014-12-01|2014-12-07.description:
A government plot leads Mulder to ponder his early days as a cadet at Quantico, including his relationship with Diana Fowley and the fateful day that he found the iconic “I Want to Believe” poster. But the intrigue goes even further back in time, to when Bill Mulder was partnered with the Cigarette Smoking Man.

Pokémon Keldeo learns something surprising! Meanwhile, the Pokémon League is under attack by Team Plasma and...their castle?! Who will drive Team Plasma out—not to mention rescue all the kidnapped Gym Leaders? Not Black...because now that he’s awakened Reshiram, he’s got another battle to fight!

Is Black ready to take on Legendary Pokémon Zekrom?!

Plus, meet powerful Team Plasma Pokémon Zweilous, Scolipede, Seismitoad, and Mandibuzz!

  • Adventure 62: Homecoming
  • Adventure 63: The Power of Dreams

volume.name: Amelia Cole and the Impossible Fate

2014-12-08|2014-12-14.description:
Torture, Chaos, Dinner!

Chaos Lords, Zoltakk and Phil, have conquered the city of Spirekassle, but their plans don't stop there. Enlisting the help of Pewfell, Bish and a 10 foot pole they plan to mount an expedition into the deepest, most ancient dungeons beneath the city to recover a long-lost magical artifact of limitless power.
2014-12-08|2014-12-14.name: Torture, Chaos, Dinner!

2014-12-15|2014-12-21.description:
Battle comes to Earth like never before! Humanity struggles to withstand the outer space onslaught. What will be the fate of the inhabitants of Monster Islands once it comes under attack?
